# Azure Tagging Convention

1. Detail of **operation team** who responsible for this resource

| Name                 | Description                                                  | Type   | Possible Values                      |
|----------------------|--------------------------------------------------------------|--------|--------------------------------------|
| Operation.Department | Short name of the department which operation team belongs to | String | Can be N/A if there is no Department |
| Operation.Section    | Short name of the section which operation team belongs to    | String | Can be N/A if there is no Section    |
| Operation.Unit       | Short name of the unit which operation team belongs to       | String | Can be N/A if there is no Unit       |
| Operation.Name       | Name of operation owner                                      | String | (Mandatory)                          |

2. Detail of **developer team** who responsible for this resource

| Name                 | Description                                                  | Type   | Possible Values                               |
|----------------------|--------------------------------------------------------------|--------|-----------------------------------------------|
| Developer.Department | Short name of the department which developer team belongs to | String | Can be N/A if there is no Department (Vendor) |
| Developer.Section    | Short name of the section which developer team belongs to    | String | Can be N/A if there is no Section             |
| Developer.Unit       | Short name of the unit which developer team belongs to       | String | Can be N/A if there is no Unit                |
| Developer.Name       | Name of developer owner                                      | String | (Mandatory)                                   |

3. Detail of **business team** who responsible for this resource

| Name                     | Description                                               | Type   | Possible Values                      |
|--------------------------|-----------------------------------------------------------|--------|--------------------------------------|
| BusinessOwner.Department | Shot name of the department which business team belong to | String | Can be N/A if there is no Department |
| BusinessOwner.Section    | Shot name of the section which business  team belong to   | String | Can be N/A if there is no Section    |
| BusinessOwner.Unit       | Shot name of the unit which business  team belong to      | String | Can be N/A if there is no Unit       |
| BusinessOwner.Name       | Name of business owner                                    | String | (Mandatory)                          |

4. System details

| Name                | Description                                                                                    | Type    | Possible Values                                      |
|---------------------|------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|---------|------------------------------------------------------|
| Environment         | Deployment environment of the application, workload, or service                                | Enum    | dev / sit / stg / prd / sbx (mandatory)              |
| ClusterNumber       | Order of number which the system will be deploy                                                | Integer | e.g. 1, 2, 3, … (mandatory)                          |
| CostCenter          | Budget code (can request from administration officers of each department) (Cloud consumption)  | String  | e.g. 00123, … (mandatory)                            |
| Region              | Regions of cloud provider which the resource deployed in                                       | String  | e.g. southeastasia, eastasia, …                      |
| SystemName          | Name of the workload the resource supports.                                                    | string  | e.g. SuperDuper, Donut, MyChannel, etc               |
| DataClassification  | Sensitivity of data hosted by this resource.                                                   | Enum    | Highly Confidential / Restricted / Internal / Public |
| BusinessCriticality | Business impact of the resource or supported workload.                                         | Enum    | High / Medium / Low                                  |
| CommercialName      | Commercial name of the project                                                                 | String  |                                                      |
